{"tid":1427760,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢中有野講] 罷工一役已經輸左，之後唔可以再輸","createTime":"2019-08-07T07:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T13:25:09.000Z","uid":102944,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"778832f98e94e3276aa6b00e142ac670aa8a3f53","tid":1427760,"uid":102944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:39:41.000Z","msg":"我係一個廢中，六月到而家都出黎好多次，但希望嚟緊呢番說話唔會俾人當我係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早兩個月大家得出「勇武為劍，和理為盾」，仲要「和理非-&gt;set deadline-&gt;勇武」，我哋用呢個方向經歷咗好多嘢，<span style=\"color: red;\">直到早兩日大罷工，真係唔覺得有贏到</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 幾乎冇乜媒體報道罷工個情況</span><br />\n好似好多人罷工，但係連張相都睇唔到，人數都係琴日聽民間記招先知30萬人， 啲媒體淨係報道我哋點樣勇武，好少睇到啲和平集會嘅畫面，<span style=\"color: red;\">其實不利外國媒體報道</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 狗有心挑釁我哋，但係我哋冇守好</span><br />\n慶幸和理非對武力的接受程度慢慢提高，好多地方佔咗路都得到佢地支持。但好明顯星期一嘅感覺就係d狗有心引班勇武出黎，令到罷工失焦。<span style=\"color: red;\">分唔到活動係和理非主力定勇武主力</span>星期一有罷工都知道好多好似阿叔我咁嘅年紀d人出黎，好多人本身都諗住係集會係和理非，但係手足好快就去咗圍狗屋，堵路...<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">如果星期一罷工定性係勇武，我都會出嚟，都會支持 ;但係如果係和理非，希望手足可以忍一忍手，因為我好多朋友都唔知當日仲應唔應該留低支持。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">問題重點係我哋而家慢慢冇咗「和理非-&gt;set deadline-&gt;勇武」呢套打法</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而家完全係遊行-&gt;留守-&gt;打-&gt;幾位手足俾狗拉</span>其實真係好心痛每次都冇左幾位手足<br />\n條八婆仲要出黎扣帽子，<span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋就嚟輸啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">依家係要講返我哋嘅訴求，同埋迫嗰條八婆面對！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n頭先睇出邊啲人話每個禮拜三係行動嘅轉捩點，希望今個星期真係跟返上兩個月嘅打法，唔想冇左一手好牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"7b39c4cd242e864c6b0b993d4c338f09c197176c","tid":1427760,"uid":102944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:40:00.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"5e6b76407576ec47a1fbc070b2f3dd7d1429dde3","tid":1427760,"uid":102944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216b67dbeb84b341fa2ee6fed6e325531f5c6d8b","tid":1427760,"uid":102944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee02ac02b508126963e77258a7d009a9afa4b7b5","tid":1427760,"uid":102944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6930ae5ecf3718391df58b91b17e4aa36520d0","tid":1427760,"uid":166405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:41:40.000Z","msg":"勇武真係休息下，依家拉左過百人，驚唔夠人捱到去十月一"},{"pid":"397fa1bf2e5523ae680db0c352b81835c397dcfb","tid":1427760,"uid":102944,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"af6930ae5ecf3718391df58b91b17e4aa36520d0","tid":1427760,"uid":166405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:41:40.000Z","msg":"勇武真係休息下，依家拉左過百人，驚唔夠人捱到去十月一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:42:16.000Z","msg":"唔係叫勇武休息，而係大家要分好工"},{"pid":"0782fcfaaec2530ac188c113779426dc34c421f0","tid":1427760,"uid":166273,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:43:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其實我覺得快閃真係work，班狗追唔切之餘又可以嘥佢地時，拉少一個得一個。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Be smoke</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4fac16477772944b03632c8bdd2440533d3ff330","tid":1427760,"uid":166273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:43:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: large;\">其實我覺得快閃真係work，班狗追唔切之餘又可以嘥佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">時間</span>，拉少一個得一個。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Be smoke</span></strong></blockquote>"},{"pid":"20defb9d0422b505d294e6efd9831aa507cbe913","tid":1427760,"uid":274414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"幫推, 我都開咗個post講類似同一樣野"},{"pid":"11297e1c853a116abc74d3fa71f2a20526e4fd0e","tid":1427760,"uid":102944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:44:50.000Z","msg":"推，希望比多人見到"},{"pid":"b38570048973361cd3d0af8e030feaa40c443852","tid":1427760,"uid":102944,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0782fcfaaec2530ac188c113779426dc34c421f0","tid":1427760,"uid":166273,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:43:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其實我覺得快閃真係work，班狗追唔切之餘又可以嘥佢地時，拉少一個得一個。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Be smoke</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:49:37.000Z","msg":"快閃係其中一種打法，但係個問題係而家連集會都冇咗焦點，啲嘢太快去咗勇武嗰邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b23876fc8ed1763abedc4079f688b1136130a0","tid":1427760,"uid":102944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f72229ee542d3f20db57620cd9e997a93a5798","tid":1427760,"uid":102944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:04:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d01a93029608d0c38eb747a691c71b7f139da66","tid":1427760,"uid":102944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:07:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1bd3f8d3f6385dcd417c63ae85acc5c3ac6edc6","tid":1427760,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675895dd55a0b0e6337fd78150d12c39561b2179","tid":1427760,"uid":299675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"我認為大家可以休息反幾日，整反個和理非only 集會，重新凝聚反大家既力量，張個focus重新聚焦反係我地個5大訴求，回應反中共同廢柴政府一直既扭曲道理。尋日個d記者會都見到，佢地根本唔係想解決問題，只係想解決我地同滅聲。要比全香港，全中國同全世界人睇到香港既示威者唔係暴徒，大家好團結，訴求都好清晰，盲目不仁同暴力既係政府。<br />\n<br />\n不是割蓆，只係覺得連日黎既武力鎮壓好似真係將成件事既focus blur左，覺得要眾焦反去問題既基本面上。<br />\n<br />\n感覺到社會上(特別係國際社會上)既輿論focus已經唔再係我地既5大訴求。"},{"pid":"26b9779c9adb9ebb9d3d40bb3e21137a867c5b60","tid":1427760,"uid":102944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:18:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ffc555ce44cc0e54dd4eba95e61dcd5df34cecc","tid":1427760,"uid":102944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:50:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5ba413d02d022af1e2cd9d33876982656dad2b2","tid":1427760,"uid":146813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:59:35.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\n打法好緊要"},{"pid":"49648050b2c8ecc49e08ced1370d55854be14fc7","tid":1427760,"uid":102944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5ba413d02d022af1e2cd9d33876982656dad2b2","tid":1427760,"uid":146813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:59:35.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\n打法好緊要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:59:54.000Z","msg":"謝"},{"pid":"b803296d4c8f4f7696e86df44eedb09c2281bca3","tid":1427760,"uid":104908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6cc8f17ca072aa5047e79f14e5287595509f91","tid":1427760,"uid":104908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ca02d901c4f5d26897de76159d1b478b6ab695","tid":1427760,"uid":102944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e0ec2a0b97bad81cf0f5566cb1c9367cff